: 841, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"global unity\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"host cities\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee (IOC) routinely makes grandiose claims about its commitment to humanity.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"grandiose claims\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"its commitment\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"humanity\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking over theOlympic Charterand the IOC's guiding philosophy of \\\"Olympism,\\\" it's hard not to be struck by the organization's promises, however empty they may be.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1097, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.018121785233279e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Charterand\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympism\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"the organization's promises\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It states: \\\"The goal of Olympism is to place sport at the service of the harmonious development of humankind, with a view to promoting a peaceful society concerned with the preservation of human dignity.\\\"\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The goal\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympism\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"the service\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"the harmonious development\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"humankind\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"a view\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"a peaceful society\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"the preservation\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"human dignity\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet,time and again, the Games have further disadvantaged some of the world's most marginalized people in host cities.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's most marginalized people\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"host cities\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Paris 2024, the outcome will be no different.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1553, \"end\": 1563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.301351386448287e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nations of the world will look the other way, ignore the consequences of the Games and celebrate a new crop of athletes - fulfilling the Olympic's motto of \\\"faster, higher, stronger\\\" - while embracing displacement, gentrification and bigotry.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The nations\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"the consequences\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"a new crop\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic's motto\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"gentrification\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"bigotry\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In April, hundreds of people, including displaced communities,were evictedfrom makeshift shelters in a camp south of Paris.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1964, \"end\": 1969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999690948421616, \"rank\": 3.090611319287601e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"displaced communities\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"evictedfrom makeshift shelters\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"a camp\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is only the most recent example; police have carried outnumerous evictionsin therun-up to the Games.\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only the most recent example\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2015}, {\"ngram\": \"outnumerous evictionsin therun-up\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These evictions are a clear example of how the Olympic Games are used as a pretext to displace marginalized people to sanitize a host city's image beforethe global spectacle.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These evictions\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"a clear example\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2138}, {\"ngram\": \"a pretext\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"marginalized people\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"a host city's image\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"beforethe global spectacle\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities say the evictions arenot connected to the Games.\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2314, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Authorities\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"the evictions\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, in July 2023, a new law was passed imposing large fines and prison sentences for illegal occupation.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"a new law\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2347}, {\"ngram\": \"large fines\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2379}, {\"ngram\": \"prison sentences\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"illegal occupation\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Displaced communities encounter significantmental health risks, which primarily arise from theirprior experiences of false persecution,warand having to leave theirhome countries.\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Displaced communities\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"significantmental health risks\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"theirprior experiences\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2539}, {\"ngram\": \"false persecution\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"theirhome countries\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The prolonged migration process inEuropean countriesfurther exacerbates the risk of displaced communities experiencing mental health symptoms and disorders.\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prolonged migration process\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"inEuropean countriesfurther\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2664}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2685}, {\"ngram\": \"displaced communities\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health symptoms\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"disorders\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Research further showsthat factors like unstable living conditions, and the breakdown of social and cultural ties further compound vulnerability, increasing the risk of mental health symptoms and disorders amongdisplaced communities.\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"further showsthat factors\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"unstable living conditions\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"the breakdown\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2848}, {\"ngram\": \"social and cultural ties further compound vulnerability\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2928}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health symptoms\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2954}, {\"ngram\": \"disorders\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"communities\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 2995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Forcing people to leave the only places they can find shelter to accommodate events like the Olympic Games only compounds the trauma many have already experienced.\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"the only places\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"shelter\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3059}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3104}, {\"ngram\": \"the trauma\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French government's stance on French Muslim women athleteswearing hijabsremains one of the most contentious issues surrounding the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3167, \"end\": 3173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9858621550426128, \"rank\": 0.012459676851875533, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3197, \"end\": 3203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9858621550426128, \"rank\": 0.012459676851875533, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3204, \"end\": 3210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"score\": 0.7910385495601301, \"rank\": 0.26416087822154305, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most contentious issues\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3281}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In September 2023, French Sports MinisterAmelie Oudea-Casterareiterated that French athletes will be banned from wearing hijab.\", \"from\": 3315, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3392, \"end\": 3398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9858621550426128, \"rank\": 0.012459676851875533, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"hijab\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That casts doubt on how inclusive the Paris Games will be.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"doubt\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French government's ideological view regarding religious symbols directly conflicts with the IOC's regulations that permit athletes to express their religious beliefs, including wearing religious attirelike the hijab.\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3507, \"end\": 3513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9858621550426128, \"rank\": 0.012459676851875533, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3600, \"end\": 3603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.018121785233279e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"religious symbols\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3571}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3638}, {\"ngram\": \"their religious beliefs\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3673}, {\"ngram\": \"religious attirelike\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3713}, {\"ngram\": \"the hijab\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheUnited Nations Human Rights OfficeandAmnesty Internationalhave said such bans infringe on Muslim women's rights and freedom.\", \"from\": 3726, \"to\": 3853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3819, \"end\": 3825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"score\": 0.7910385495601301, \"rank\": 0.26416087822154305, \"text\": 