dia portrayed English cricketer Azeem Rafiq's allegations of racism against the Yorkshire County Cricket Club.\", \"from\": 5221, \"to\": 5381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5261, \"end\": 5268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9780221699857519, \"rank\": 0.02200385627878925, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 5285, \"end\": 5292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_language\", \"score\": 0.9530643050218779, \"rank\": 0.049246468043395115, \"text\": \"English\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_language\"}, {\"begin\": 5303, \"end\": 5314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azeem_Rafiq\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Azeem Rafiq\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azeem_Rafiq\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azeem_Rafiq\"}, {\"begin\": 5351, \"end\": 5380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorkshire_County_Cricket_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yorkshire County Cricket Club\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorkshire_County_Cricket_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorkshire_County_Cricket_Club\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"instance\", \"from\": 5225, \"to\": 5233}, {\"ngram\": \"racism\", \"from\": 5332, \"to\": 5338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The media narrative suggested that British society is aware of racism, accepts criticism and is ready to act.\", \"from\": 5382, \"to\": 5491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5417, \"end\": 5432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_society\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British society\", \"types\": [], \"wik